# Project Name
RPI4 fitness tracker - old school website edition

## Overview
This provides a mobile friendly website that records basic records of how one's 
fitness journey is going. It generates a sqlite3 database that can be used to
generate graphics and other data visualizations for historical trending.

### Key Features
* should only require apache2, php8.2, and [data visualization]

## Quick Start 
Pull all files
Have apt install apache2, php8.2
php init_db.php
Then, load website in mobile app at http://[server location]/fitness_tracker/

## Project Purpose
Software should be free for all people.
For those who are able, then they should contribute back.
This is primarily a way for me to test out vibe coding, which is a recent trend
in 2025 as I write this. Most code is written with chatgpt5.1-instant. Any
important prompts, I will push either as commit messages or this README

